<item>
            <title>[LU-5550] LFSCK 5: Migrate the name entry from one MDT to another MDT if the name hash does not match the striped directory</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5550</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The namespace LFSCK will check whether the name hash for the name entry under the slave of striped directory matches such shard or not. If not, the LFSCK should migrate the name entry from current MDT to the right MDT. This should be done with async commit supported from DNE2 to avoid lost the name entry or duplicate the name entry and some other recovery troubles.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="26192">LU-5550</key>
            <summary>LFSCK 5: Migrate the name entry from one MDT to another MDT if the name hash does not match the striped directory</summary>
